    "body": "<h3> Problem description </h3>\n<p>\n\tAs the September has already ended, so Kutkut goes to his girlfriend to ask her for a date, but to his surprise the girlfriend is already awake and is doing some assignment. As she is not good at programming she asks him to help her complete the assignment as soon as possible. The assignment question is follows:\n\t</p>\n<p>Given a rooted tree having nodes from 1 to N(rooted at 1) with all nodes empty initially. However, each node may contain one diamond max.The question asks following two types of queries - <br />\n<strong>0 x </strong>Go to the node x and change the state of all the nodes in the subtree of x(including node x) <br />\n<strong>1 x </strong>Count the number of Diamonds in the Subtree rooted at x \n</p>\n<p>\nThe change in state is given as<br />\nIf the node contains a diamond then remove the diamond from there else add 1 diamond to it.\n</p>\n<p>\nKutkut's girlfriend has put forward condition that he must help her solve this question before going on the date.<br />\nKutkut doesn't know how to program but he desperately needs to go on this date. Can you help him?\n</p>\n\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p>\nThe first line of input contains two numbers <strong>N</strong> and <strong>Q</strong>, where <strong>N</strong> is the number of Nodes and <strong>Q</strong> is the number of Queries.<br />\nFollowing <strong>N-1</strong> lines contain two numbers <strong>u, v</strong> stating that there is an edge from node <strong>u</strong> to node <strong>v</strong>.<br />\nThe next <strong>Q</strong> line contains two numbers in the form<br />\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<strong>0 x</strong>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0(change the state)<br />\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<strong>1 x</strong>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0(count the diamonds)</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p>For each query of the form <strong>1 x</strong>, output the <strong>number of diamonds</strong> in the subtree of <strong>x</strong> (including x).</p>\n\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>1</strong> &lt;= <strong>N</strong> &lt;= <strong>10^5</strong></li>\n<li><strong>1</strong> &lt;= <strong>Q</strong> &lt;= <strong>10^5</strong></li>\n<li><strong>1</strong> &lt;= <strong>u</strong>, <strong>v</strong> &lt;= <strong>N</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input:</b>\n3 3\n1 2\n1 3\n0 2\n0 3\n1 1\n\n<b>Output:</b>\n2\n</pre><p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Explanation</h3>\n<pre>\n\t \t    1(0)\t\t\t      1(0)\t\t\t\t      1(0)\n\t \t   /      \\\t           -->      /      \\            -->               /      \\\n\t        2(0)     3(0)                 2(1)    3(0)                      2(1)     3(1)\n\n\t\t INITIAL \t\t         1st UPDATE\t\t\t 2nd UPDATE\n\n     0 : No diamond\n     1 : Diamond\n</pre>",
